<% title "Contact" %>

<h3>We Want to hear from you!</h3>

<p>Do you have Questions, Comments and/or Concers about an event or trail? Let us know we want to help. </p>
<p>If you are having issuse with the registration form you can call the Rangely Chambers durring business hours at (970) 675-5290.</p>
<p>After business hour please send us an Email
  and we will reach out to you the next business day.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

<form action="mailto:rangelychamber@gmail.com" method="post">
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="NAME" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Name:</label>
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-md" id="NAME" placeholder="Full Name">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="EMAIL" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Email:</label>
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <input type="email" class="form-control form-control-md" id="EMAIL" placeholder="Email Address">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <label for="MESSAGE" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Message:</label>
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <input type="textarea" class="form-control form-control-md" rows="5" id="MESSAGE">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-group row">
    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Sign in</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</form>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
